<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$guan-mao-12" href="/people/guan-mao-12">关毛</a>，<strong title="唉！" class="zu-question-my-bio">唉！</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="283">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhao-zhen-dian" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhao-zhen-dian" class="zg-link" title="赵真典">赵真典</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$huchong-ling" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/huchong-ling" class="zg-link" title="huchong ling">huchong ling</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$dddddd-liu" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/dddddd-liu" class="zg-link" title="王八狮子甲">王八狮子甲</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="4182380" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">我本燕赵士，忝列刘氏裔。<br>唯存匡扶志，白身抗贼军。 <br>朝辞下邳国，暮登新野城。 <br>千军尽折损，百战无寸功。<br>阿瞒乱中原，碧眼据江东。 <br>忍看社稷覆，大道不见明。<br>功业未及建，髀肉已复生。<br>揽辔长叹息，寄身在蜀中。<br>远念高帝志，王道不苟存。<br>奋起虎贲士，功成得汉宁。<br>云长走荆州，翼德丧奸人。<br>怒发冲冠冕，遗恨失夷陵。<br>今困白帝城，泪将付孔明。<br>舍身岂不易，无颜见祖宗。<br>悲夫交华盖，苍天实难恨！
<a href="/question/29999854/answer/46375169" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
